reviewtext: I have been using Belkin Cat5 cables for a long time.They come with a stamp and specs on the wire and the connectors have a Belkin logo embedded in them.The one i received does not have the Belkin name anywhere on the wire and the connectors.Sure its a fake.If i had to buy any Cat5e i could have spent only $10 including shipping.May be this fake cable works good, but the seller should not deceive people by saying its a Belkin cable.Buyer beware.
